<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>n8n AI Social Media Automation — Assignment Submission</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=JetBrains+Mono:wght@400;700&family=Syne:wght@400;600;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
  :root {
    --bg: #0a0a0f;
    --surface: #111118;
    --card: #16161f;
    --border: #2a2a3a;
    --accent: #7c6dfa;
    --accent2: #fa6d8c;
    --accent3: #6dfabc;
    --accent4: #fac06d;
    --text: #e8e8f0;
    --muted: #6b6b80;
    --code-bg: #0d0d15;
  }
  * { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
  html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }
  body {
    font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif;
    background: var(--bg);
    color: var(--text);
    line-height: 1.6;
    min-height: 100vh;
  }

  /* ── Header ── */
  .header {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0f0f1a 0%, #1a0f2e 50%, #0f1a1a 100%);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    padding: 60px 40px 50px;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .header::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: -80px; right: -80px;
    width: 400px; height: 400px;
    background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(124,109,250,0.15) 0%, transparent 70%);
    pointer-events: none;
  }
  .header::after {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    bottom: -60px; left: -60px;
    width: 300px; height: 300px;
    background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(109,250,188,0.08) 0%, transparent 70%);
    pointer-events: none;
  }
  .header-tag {
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 11px;
    color: var(--accent3);
    letter-spacing: 3px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 8px;
  }
  .header-tag::before {
    content: '';
    display: inline-block;
    width: 24px; height: 1px;
    background: var(--accent3);
  }
  .header h1 {
    font-size: clamp(32px, 5vw, 56px);
    font-weight: 800;
    line-height: 1.1;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }
  .header h1 span { color: var(--accent); }
  .header-meta {
    display: flex;
    gap: 24px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    margin-top: 24px;
  }
  .meta-badge {
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 12px;
    padding: 6px 14px;
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 4px;
    color: var(--muted);
  }
  .meta-badge span { color: var(--text); }

  /* ── Nav ── */
  .nav {
    position: sticky;
    top: 0;
    z-index: 100;
    background: rgba(10,10,15,0.92);
    backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    padding: 0 40px;
    display: flex;
    gap: 0;
    overflow-x: auto;
  }
  .nav a {
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 12px;
    color: var(--muted);
    text-decoration: none;
    padding: 16px 20px;
    white-space: nowrap;
    border-bottom: 2px solid transparent;
    transition: all 0.2s;
  }
  .nav a:hover { color: var(--text); border-bottom-color: var(--accent); }

  /* ── Layout ── */
  .container { max-width: 1100px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 60px 40px; }
  .section { margin-bottom: 80px; }
  .section-header {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 16px;
    margin-bottom: 32px;
    padding-bottom: 16px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  }
  .section-num {
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 11px;
    color: var(--accent);
    background: rgba(124,109,250,0.1);
    border: 1px solid rgba(124,109,250,0.3);
    padding: 4px 10px;
    border-radius: 4px;
  }
  .section h2 { font-size: 28px; font-weight: 700; }

  /* ── Cards ── */
  .card {
    background: var(--card);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 28px;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }
  .card-title {
    font-size: 14px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--accent);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 1px;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
  }

  /* ── Workflow diagram ── */
  .flow {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0;
  }
  .flow-row {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 8px;
    margin-bottom: 4px;
  }
  .flow-node {
    background: var(--code-bg);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 14px 20px;
    flex: 1;
    position: relative;
  }
  .flow-node.trigger { border-color: var(--accent3); }
  .flow-node.ai { border-color: var(--accent); }
  .flow-node.image { border-color: var(--accent2); }
  .flow-node.post { border-color: var(--accent4); }
  .flow-node.log { border-color: var(--accent3); }
  .flow-node.error-node { border-color: #fa4d4d; }
  .node-label {
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 11px;
    color: var(--muted);
    margin-bottom: 4px;
  }
  .node-name { font-weight: 700; font-size: 15px; }
  .flow-node.trigger .node-name { color: var(--accent3); }
  .flow-node.ai .node-name { color: var(--accent); }
  .flow-node.image .node-name { color: var(--accent2); }
  .flow-node.post .node-name { color: var(--accent4); }
  .flow-node.log .node-name { color: var(--accent3); }
  .flow-node.error-node .node-name { color: #fa4d4d; }
  .flow-arrow {
    width: 2px;
    height: 28px;
    background: var(--border);
    margin: 0 auto;
    position: relative;
  }
  .flow-arrow::after {
    content: '▼';
    position: absolute;
    bottom: -8px;
    left: 50%;
    transform: translateX(-50%);
    font-size: 10px;
    color: var(--muted);
  }
  .flow-parallel {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 16px;
    margin: 4px 0;
  }
  .parallel-label {
    text-align: center;
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 11px;
    color: var(--muted);
    margin: 8px 0;
  }

  /* ── Code blocks ── */
  pre, code {
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 13px;
  }
  pre {
    background: var(--code-bg);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 20px;
    overflow-x: auto;
    margin: 16px 0;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }
  code { color: var(--accent3); }
  .k { color: var(--accent); }
  .s { color: var(--accent4); }
  .c { color: var(--muted); font-style: italic; }
  .n { color: var(--accent2); }

  /* ── API Steps ── */
  .api-step {
    display: flex;
    gap: 20px;
    margin-bottom: 28px;
    align-items: flex-start;
  }
  .step-num {
    width: 32px;
    height: 32px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: rgba(124,109,250,0.15);
    border: 1px solid rgba(124,109,250,0.4);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 12px;
    color: var(--accent);
    flex-shrink: 0;
    margin-top: 2px;
  }
  .step-content h4 { font-size: 16px; margin-bottom: 8px; }
  .step-content p { color: var(--muted); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6; }

  /* ── Credentials table ── */
  .cred-table { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; margin-top: 16px; }
  .cred-table th {
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 11px;
    color: var(--muted);
    text-align: left;
    padding: 10px 16px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 1px;
  }
  .cred-table td {
    padding: 12px 16px;
    font-size: 14px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(42,42,58,0.5);
    vertical-align: top;
  }
  .cred-table tr:hover td { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.02); }
  .cred-table code {
    font-size: 12px;
    background: var(--code-bg);
    padding: 2px 8px;
    border-radius: 4px;
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
  }
  .tag-accent { color: var(--accent); font-weight: 700; }
  .tag-green { color: var(--accent3); }
  .tag-pink { color: var(--accent2); }
  .tag-yellow { color: var(--accent4); }

  /* ── Test cases ── */
  .test-case { margin-bottom: 32px; }
  .tc-header {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 12px;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }
  .tc-id {
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 11px;
    padding: 4px 10px;
    border-radius: 4px;
    font-weight: 700;
  }
  .tc-id.pass { background: rgba(109,250,188,0.1); color: var(--accent3); border: 1px solid rgba(109,250,188,0.3); }
  .tc-id.fail { background: rgba(250,77,77,0.1); color: #fa4d4d; border: 1px solid rgba(250,77,77,0.3); }
  .tc-id.error { background: rgba(250,192,109,0.1); color: var(--accent4); border: 1px solid rgba(250,192,109,0.3); }
  .tc-name { font-size: 18px; font-weight: 700; }
  .tc-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 16px; }
  @media (max-width: 700px) { .tc-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } }
  .tc-box {
    background: var(--code-bg);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 16px;
  }
  .tc-box-label {
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 10px;
    color: var(--muted);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 2px;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
  }
  .check-list { list-style: none; }
  .check-list li {
    font-size: 13px;
    padding: 4px 0;
    display: flex;
    gap: 8px;
    align-items: flex-start;
  }
  .check-list .ok { color: var(--accent3); }
  .check-list .fail { color: #fa4d4d; }

  /* ── Issues ── */
  .issue-card {
    background: var(--card);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-left: 3px solid var(--accent2);
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 20px 24px;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }
  .issue-title { font-size: 16px; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 8px; }
  .issue-desc { color: var(--muted); font-size: 14px; margin-bottom: 12px; }
  .issue-fix {
    font-size: 13px;
    background: rgba(109,250,188,0.05);
    border: 1px solid rgba(109,250,188,0.2);
    border-radius: 6px;
    padding: 10px 14px;
  }
  .issue-fix strong { color: var(--accent3); }

  /* ── ENV section ── */
  .env-group { margin-bottom: 24px; }
  .env-group-title {
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 11px;
    color: var(--accent);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 2px;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
    padding-bottom: 8px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(124,109,250,0.2);
  }
  .env-row {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 260px 1fr;
    gap: 12px;
    padding: 8px 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(42,42,58,0.3);
    font-size: 13px;
    align-items: start;
  }
  .env-key {
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    color: var(--accent4);
  }
  .env-val { color: var(--muted); font-size: 12px; }
  .env-val.ok::before { content: '✓ '; color: var(--accent3); }
  .env-val.warn::before { content: '⚠ '; color: var(--accent4); }

  /* ── Footer ── */
  .footer {
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
    padding: 40px;
    text-align: center;
    color: var(--muted);
    font-size: 13px;
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<!-- HEADER -->
<div class="header">
  <div class="header-tag">Final Selection Round — Assignment</div>
  <h1>n8n <span>AI Social Media</span><br>Automation Workflow</h1>
  <p style="color: var(--muted); max-width: 600px; font-size: 15px;">
    End-to-end automation: Gemini 1.5 Pro → Leonardo AI → Facebook + Instagram posting → Google Sheets logging.
    Built with n8n, REST APIs, and zero paid infrastructure.
  </p>
  <div class="header-meta">
    <div class="meta-badge">Round: <span>Final Selection</span></div>
    <div class="meta-badge">Platforms: <span>Facebook + Instagram</span></div>
    <div class="meta-badge">AI: <span>Gemini 1.5 Pro + Leonardo AI</span></div>
    <div class="meta-badge">Logging: <span>Google Sheets</span></div>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- NAV -->
<nav class="nav">
  <a href="#workflow">① Workflow</a>
  <a href="#env">② Environment</a>
  <a href="#credentials">③ Credentials</a>
  <a href="#api-docs">④ API Docs</a>
  <a href="#tests">⑤ Test Cases</a>
  <a href="#issues">⑥ Issues & Notes</a>
</nav>

<div class="container">

  <!-- ───────────────────────────────────────── -->
  <!-- SECTION 1: WORKFLOW -->
  <!-- ───────────────────────────────────────── -->
  <section class="section" id="workflow">
    <div class="section-header">
      <span class="section-num">DELIVERABLE 01</span>
      <h2>n8n Workflow Architecture</h2>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
      <div class="card-title">Node Flow — End to End</div>
      <div class="flow">

        <div class="flow-row">
          <div class="flow-node trigger">
            <div class="node-label">TRIGGER</div>
            <div class="node-name">🌐 Webhook — POST /social-media-trigger</div>
            <div style="color:var(--muted);font-size:12px;margin-top:4px">Receives: topic, brand, tone, platforms[]</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="flow-arrow"></div>

        <div class="flow-row">
          <div class="flow-node ai">
            <div class="node-label">VALIDATION</div>
            <div class="node-name">🔍 Input Validator (Code Node)</div>
            <div style="color:var(--muted);font-size:12px;margin-top:4px">Checks required fields → throws error if missing</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="flow-arrow"></div>

        <div class="flow-row">
          <div class="flow-node ai">
            <div class="node-label">AI CONTENT</div>
            <div class="node-name">🤖 Gemini 1.5 Pro — Content Generator</div>
            <div style="color:var(--muted);font-size:12px;margin-top:4px">Generates: captions × 4 platforms, hashtags, CTAs, image prompt</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="flow-arrow"></div>

        <div class="flow-row">
          <div class="flow-node ai">
            <div class="node-label">PARSER</div>
            <div class="node-name">⚙️ Parse Gemini Response (Code Node)</div>
            <div style="color:var(--muted);font-size:12px;margin-top:4px">Strips markdown fences → JSON.parse → extracts image_prompt</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="flow-arrow"></div>

        <div class="flow-row">
          <div class="flow-node image">
            <div class="node-label">IMAGE GENERATION</div>
            <div class="node-name">🎨 Leonardo AI — Generate Image</div>
            <div style="color:var(--muted);font-size:12px;margin-top:4px">POST /generations → 1024×1024 image, model: Leonardo Diffusion XL</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="flow-arrow"></div>

        <div class="flow-row">
          <div class="flow-node image">
            <div class="node-label">WAIT</div>
            <div class="node-name">⏱ Wait 15s → Fetch Image Result</div>
            <div style="color:var(--muted);font-size:12px;margin-top:4px">GET /generations/{id} → extract CDN image URL</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="flow-arrow"></div>

        <div class="flow-row">
          <div class="flow-node ai">
            <div class="node-label">MERGE</div>
            <div class="node-name">🔗 Merge Content + Image URL</div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="parallel-label">── PARALLEL POSTING ──</div>
        <div class="flow-parallel">
          <div class="flow-node post">
            <div class="node-label">PLATFORM 1</div>
            <div class="node-name">📘 Post to Facebook</div>
            <div style="color:var(--muted);font-size:12px;margin-top:4px">POST /v18.0/{pageId}/photos with caption + hashtags + CTA</div>
          </div>
          <div>
            <div class="flow-node post" style="margin-bottom:8px">
              <div class="node-label">PLATFORM 2 — STEP 1</div>
              <div class="node-name">📸 Instagram Create Container</div>
            </div>
            <div class="flow-node post">
              <div class="node-label">PLATFORM 2 — STEP 2</div>
              <div class="node-name">📸 Instagram Publish</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="flow-arrow"></div>

        <div class="flow-row">
          <div class="flow-node ai">
            <div class="node-label">AGGREGATE</div>
            <div class="node-name">📊 Aggregate Results (Code Node)</div>
            <div style="color:var(--muted);font-size:12px;margin-top:4px">Collects all post IDs, statuses, errors</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="flow-arrow"></div>

        <div class="flow-row">
          <div class="flow-node log">
            <div class="node-label">LOGGING</div>
            <div class="node-name">📋 Log to Google Sheets — "Social Media Logs"</div>
            <div style="color:var(--muted);font-size:12px;margin-top:4px">24 columns: all captions, hashtags, post IDs, statuses</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="flow-arrow"></div>

        <div class="flow-row">
          <div class="flow-node trigger">
            <div class="node-label">RESPONSE</div>
            <div class="node-name">✅ Respond to Webhook — JSON success response</div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div style="margin-top:24px;padding-top:20px;border-top:1px dashed var(--border)">
          <div class="flow-row">
            <div class="flow-node error-node">
              <div class="node-label">ERROR PATH (any node failure)</div>
              <div class="node-name">🛑 Error Handler → Log Error to "Error Logs" Sheet</div>
              <div style="color:var(--muted);font-size:12px;margin-top:4px">Catches all failures: logs run_id, error_message, error_node, timestamp</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
      <div class="card-title">Webhook Payload Structure</div>
      <pre><span class="c">// POST http://localhost:5678/webhook/social-media-trigger</span>
{
  <span class="k">"topic"</span>:     <span class="s">"AI tools for students in 2025"</span>,   <span class="c">// required</span>
  <span class="k">"brand"</span>:     <span class="s">"TechLearn"</span>,                       <span class="c">// optional (default: "Your Brand")</span>
  <span class="k">"tone"</span>:      <span class="s">"motivational"</span>,                    <span class="c">// optional (default: "professional")</span>
  <span class="k">"platforms"</span>: [<span class="s">"facebook"</span>, <span class="s">"instagram"</span>]       <span class="c">// optional</span>
}</pre>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ───────────────────────────────────────── -->
  <!-- SECTION 2: ENV -->
  <!-- ───────────────────────────────────────── -->
  <section class="section" id="env">
    <div class="section-header">
      <span class="section-num">DELIVERABLE 02</span>
      <h2>Environment Variables — Verification</h2>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
      <div class="card-title">Your .env File — Status Check</div>

      <div class="env-group">
        <div class="env-group-title">n8n Core</div>
        <div class="env-row"><div class="env-key">N8N_HOST</div><div class="env-val ok">localhost — correct for local dev</div></div>
        <div class="env-row"><div class="env-key">N8N_PORT</div><div class="env-val ok">5678 — correct default port</div></div>
        <div class="env-row"><div class="env-key">N8N_PROTOCOL</div><div class="env-val ok">http — correct for local</div></div>
        <div class="env-row"><div class="env-key">WEBHOOK_URL</div><div class="env-val ok">http://localhost:5678/webhook/social-media-trigger — matches workflow</div></div>
        <div class="env-row"><div class="env-key">N8N_ENCRYPTION_KEY</div><div class="env-val warn">FILL THIS — generate with: <code>openssl rand -hex 16</code></div></div>
      </div>

      <div class="env-group">
        <div class="env-group-title">Google Gemini</div>
        <div class="env-row"><div class="env-key">GEMINI_API_KEY</div><div class="env-val warn">Fill from aistudio.google.com → Get API Key</div></div>
        <div class="env-row"><div class="env-key">GEMINI_MODEL</div><div class="env-val ok">gemini-1.5-pro — correct</div></div>
      </div>

      <div class="env-group">
        <div class="env-group-title">Leonardo AI</div>
        <div class="env-row"><div class="env-key">LEONARDO_API_KEY</div><div class="env-val warn">Fill from app.leonardo.ai → Account Settings → API Access</div></div>
        <div class="env-row"><div class="env-key">LEONARDO_MODEL_ID</div><div class="env-val ok">b24e16ff-06e3-43eb-8d33-4416c2d75876 — Leonardo Diffusion XL, correct</div></div>
        <div class="env-row"><div class="env-key">LEONARDO_IMAGE_WIDTH/HEIGHT</div><div class="env-val ok">1024×1024 — correct for both Facebook & Instagram</div></div>
      </div>

      <div class="env-group">
        <div class="env-group-title">Facebook</div>
        <div class="env-row"><div class="env-key">FACEBOOK_PAGE_ACCESS_TOKEN</div><div class="env-val warn">Fill from Graph API Explorer — must be LONG-LIVED (60 days)</div></div>
        <div class="env-row"><div class="env-key">FACEBOOK_PAGE_ID</div><div class="env-val warn">Fill — GET /me/accounts → copy "id" for your Page</div></div>
