        </div>
      </div>
      <pre><span class="c"># Test your key works:</span>
curl -X POST <span class="s">"https://generativelanguage.googleapis.com/v1beta/models/gemini-1.5-pro:generateContent?key=YOUR_KEY"</span> \
  -H <span class="s">"Content-Type: application/json"</span> \
  -d <span class="s">'{"contents":[{"parts":[{"text":"Hello"}]}]}'</span></pre>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
      <div class="card-title">2. Leonardo AI API</div>
      <div class="api-step">
        <div class="step-num">1</div>
        <div class="step-content">
          <h4>Get API Key</h4>
          <p>Go to <strong>app.leonardo.ai</strong> → Account (top right) → API Access → Create New Key → Copy key</p>
