        </div>
      </div>
      <pre><span class="c"># Test Leonardo — start generation:</span>
curl -X POST <span class="s">"https://cloud.leonardo.ai/api/rest/v1/generations"</span> \
  -H <span class="s">"Authorization: Bearer YOUR_LEONARDO_KEY"</span> \
  -H <span class="s">"Content-Type: application/json"</span> \
  -d <span class="s">'{"prompt":"a beautiful sunset over mountains","width":512,"height":512,"num_images":1}'</span></pre>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
      <div class="card-title">3. Facebook + Instagram API</div>
      <div class="api-step">
        <div class="step-num">1</div>
        <div class="step-content">
          <h4>Create Meta Developer App</h4>
          <p>developers.facebook.com → My Apps → Create App → Business type → Name + email → Create</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="api-step">
        <div class="step-num">2</div>
        <div class="step-content">
          <h4>Get Long-Lived Page Token</h4>
          <p>Graph API Explorer → select app → Generate Token → grant <code>pages_manage_posts</code> + <code>pages_read_engagement</code> permissions → select your Page → copy token → exchange for long-lived:</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <pre><span class="c"># Exchange for 60-day long-lived token:</span>
curl <span class="s">"https://graph.facebook.com/oauth/access_token \
  ?grant_type=fb_exchange_token \
  &client_id=APP_ID \
  &client_secret=APP_SECRET \
  &fb_exchange_token=SHORT_LIVED_TOKEN"</span></pre>
      <div class="api-step" style="margin-top:16px">
        <div class="step-num">3</div>
        <div class="step-content">
          <h4>Get Your Page ID and Instagram User ID</h4>
          <p>Run these to get the IDs to paste into workflow node URLs:</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <pre><span class="c"># Get Page ID:</span>
curl <span class="s">"https://graph.facebook.com/me/accounts?access_token=YOUR_TOKEN"</span>

<span class="c"># Get Instagram Business User ID:</span>
curl <span class="s">"https://graph.facebook.com/{YOUR_PAGE_ID}?fields=instagram_business_account&access_token=YOUR_TOKEN"</span></pre>
    </div>

